Description:
More than meets the eye!
Positioned close to bushland and overlooking Scott's Oval, this four bedroom home is tucked away behind a tall cream picket fence. Comprising of two living areas separated by a spacious meals and kitchen, this home is sure to impress. The kitchen boasts underbench oven, gas hotplates and glass splashback. The meals area has uninterrupted views of the outdoor entertaining area and has a recycled timber feature wall that just sets the room. The master bedroom is spacious and enjoys an ensuite with an oversized double shower and large vanity with double above counter basins. The remaining three bedrooms have built in robes and are also generous in size. Climate is controlled by gas ducted heating and evaporative cooling. Externally there is a double carport with roller door to front and a sensational sized colorbond shed. The rear yard has an area for the kids to play and a firepit area for when you're entertaining. This home is very deceiving from the street and has ample room for every member of the family. Call now to arrange an inspection.

Description:
Three Bedroom Family Home
Positioned on a generous sized block close to the Murray River this three bedroom brick home is well presented and a fantastic opportunity for the first home buyer or investor. Everything about this home is oversized! The spacious kitchen and meals area features electric cooking appliances and dishwasher which overlooks the generous sized lounge room which enjoys a wood fire heater for those cool winter nights. Both spaces have feature raked ceilings with exposed beams. All three bedrooms are generous in size with BIR's with the master bedroom enjoying a large walk in robe. The family bathroom has double sized shower and vanity. Externally there is a secure single carport which allows easy vehicle access into the rear yard and garden shed. Short stroll to Thompson's Beach, this home is perfectly located for those that enjoy the walking tracks around the Murray River. Currently tenanted at $260, call for an inspection now.
